      "roundness": null,
      "text": "Validation is not one thing. A change may need tests, logs,\ntraces, dependency checks, secret checks, deployment\nvisibility, or human review. Pick the gates that fit the\nchange, and document what each one proved.",
      "originalText": "Validation is not one thing. A change may need tests, logs,\ntraces, dependency checks, secret checks, deployment\nvisibility, or human review. Pick the gates that fit the\nchange, and document what each one proved.",
